headline: Deere Isn’t the Farming Stock to Buy, Says Analyst. It’s This One.
summary: Citi analyst Kyle Menges upgraded shares of agricultural-equipment maker AGCO to Buy from Hold. He rates Deere stock at Hold.

headline: Is Deere (DE) a Buy as Wall Street Analysts Look Optimistic?
summary: The average brokerage recommendation (ABR) for Deere (DE) is equivalent to a Buy. The overly optimistic recommendations of Wall Street analysts make the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric questionable. So, is it worth buying the stock?
